       ["Feathers were reduced or lost as body size increased","conf-moderate","Skin impressions from large, derived tyrannosaurids such as Tyrannosaurus and Albertosaurus show scaly skin rather than feathers, suggesting at least some large-bodied lineages reduced their covering as they grew larger."]
